    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ToolTreaux tool pouch is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life. It features a 3 inch wide belt tunnel (belt not included) so you can easily attach it and remove it when no longer needed. Each tool belt comes with 10 different tool pouches designed to hold small, medium and large construction tools including a hammer, wrench, screwdriver, pliers, measuring tape, utility knife, pruners, trowels, levels and more. Our leather tool bags will attach to most standard belts, making this a great option for both men and women. Simply attach the bag to your favorite work or construction belt before your next hobby project</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux 10 Pocket Suede Leather Tool Pouch Hammer Drill Tool Bag</h2>\n  <p>The ToolTreaux tool pouch is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life. It features a 3 inch wide belt tunnel (belt not included) so you can easily attach it and remove it when no longer needed.</p>\n  <p>Each tool belt comes with 10 different tool pouches designed to hold small, medium and large construction tools including a hammer, wrench, screwdriver, pliers, measuring tape, utility knife, pruners, trowels, levels and more.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>HEAVY-DUTY CONSTRUCTION - ToolTreaux heavy-duty tool pouch is made of high-quality, durable and lightweight suede leather that will ensure longevity. Belt tunnel fits 3 inch wide belt (belt not included)</li>\n    <li>10 TOOL POCKETS - Tool belt comes with 10 different tool pouches made to hold different construction and hobby tools like a hammer, measuring tape, pliers, wrench, screwdriver, box cutter, level, pruners, trowels and more</li>\n    <li>ONE SIZE FITS MOST - Leather tool bag attaches to most standard belts, making it ideal for both men and women. Simply attach tool bag to your favorite work or construction belt before your next hobby project</li>\n    <li>VERSATILE TOOL BELT - Multi-use tool belt is ideal for home improvement, crafting, gardening and hobby DIY projects. Make sure you have quick access to your tools whether you’re working inside or outdoors</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Color:</strong> pink; Material: suede leather; Number of pockets: 10 (2 main, 2 medium and 6 small pockets); Belt tunnel dimensions: 3” wide; Metal tape measure clip; Steel hammer holder</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Tools/AS1101A-PNK_9_pocket_toolbelt_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"The ToolTreaux tool pouch is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> HWK106PKTB</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058481337</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Adjustable</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Our leather tool bags will attach to most standard belts, making this a great option for both men and women. Simply attach the bag to your favorite work or construction belt before your next hobby project.</p>\n  <p>Although these belts were originally designed for home improvement and construction uses, they are also great for crafting, gardening and other hobby DIY projects. Keep your tools close and organized with this belt before your next project whether it’s indoors or outdoors!</p>\n  <p>Please note: these tool belts are not customizable. Rivets may show natural sign of rust from the manufacturing process.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ToolTreaux tool pouch is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life. It features a 3 inch wide belt tunnel (belt not included) so you can easily attach it and remove it when no longer needed. Each tool belt comes with 10 different tool pouches designed to hold small, medium and large construction tools including a hammer, wrench, screwdriver, pliers, measuring tape, utility knife, pruners, trowels, levels and more. Our leather tool bags will attach to most standard belts, making this a great option for both men and women. Simply attach the bag to your favorite work or construction belt before your next hobby project.",
